General.Name: Quickstep Holdings Ltd
General.Description: Quickstep Holdings Limited manufactures advanced composites for the defense and commercial aerospace, and other industry sector customers in Australia and the United States. It also offers maintenance, repair, and overhaul services across a range of composite, bonded, and conventional metal aircraft structures to defense, government, and commercial aircraft operators. The company was incorporated in 2001 and is based in Bankstown, Australia.
